# Meteor packages used by this project, one per line.
# Check this file (and the other files in this directory) into your repository.
#
# 'meteor add' and 'meteor remove' will edit this file for you,
# but you can also edit it by hand.

## Meteor Defaults ##
meteor-base@1.0.4               # Packages every Meteor app needs to have.
mobile-experience@1.0.4         # Packages for a great mobile UX.
mongo@1.1.14                  # The database Meteor supports right now.
session@1.1.7                   # Client-side reactive dictionary for your app.
tracker@1.1.1                   # Meteor's client-side reactive programming library.
http@1.2.10                    # Make HTTP calls to remote servers
logging@1.1.16                # Logging facility.

## Compiling Tools ##
es5-shim@4.6.15               # ECMAScript 5 compatibility for older browsers.
ecmascript@0.6.1              # Enable ECMAScript2015+ syntax in app code
francocatena:compass            # Stylesheet Authoring Environment that makes your website design simpler
standard-minifier-css@1.3.2   # A minifier plugin used for Meteor apps by default.
standard-minifier-js@1.2.1    # JS minifier uses UglifyJS2.
fourseven:scss@3.8.1            # Sass build plugin for Meteor.
mquandalle:bower                # Use Bower packages in your Meteor app
meteorhacks:npm                 # Use npm modules with your Meteor App


## User Packages ##
accounts-base@1.2.14            # Meteor's user account system.
accounts-password@1.3.3         # A login service that enables secure password-based login.
alanning:roles                  # Authorization package

## Routing ##
iron:router                     # A router that works on the server and the browser.
