reywood:iron-router-ga          # Google analytics (universal edition) with some Iron Router sugar for tracking page views.
okgrow:router-autoscroll        # Smart management of scroll position across route changes for Iron and Flow Router

## Templating and UI/UX Tools ##
alethes:pages                   # State of the art, out of the box Meteor pagination
